#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "⚠️ Sensitive Content Notice"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"This module includes content that may be sensitive. You can check it out by yourself first. This will prepare you well for sharing the content with your teen and others afterwards.\n"
"\n"
"If you need support, see the “Support Contacts” section in your Library for help."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today’s topic is about teen safety.\n"
"\n"
"Teens can spend a lot of time outside the house or online, where it is harder for us to keep them safe. Talking together about safe and unsafe places — and how to prevent problems — really helps."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why is teen safety important for you and your family?"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings, everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Today our topic is teen safety \n"
"\n"
"It is our responsibility as parents to try to keep our teens safe and help them to keep themselves safe. An important part of that is that we are all aware of the safe and unsafe areas in our communities.\n"
"\n"
"It is also our responsibility to ensure that they understand the dangers that they might be exposed to when they are online. That way our teenagers will be responsible and be able to make right decisions to keep themselves safe too."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Sometimes our teens notice things about their surroundings that we don’t. By talking and listening, we can better understand their world and guide them through challenges – including the risks they face online.\n"
"\n"
"With our support, they can learn to stay safe and make good decisions. \n"
"\n"
"This guidance is important for both girls and boys. Abuse can happen in different ways — including sexual abuse."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "_Child sexual abuse can happen in different ways. It can happen when someone touches a child in a sexual way, makes sexual comments or requests, pressures or forces a child, or offers money or gifts to ask for sexual things. It can happen face-to-face or online._"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_8.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "A safety plan helped @data.characters.media_female_8.name protect her teen. Tap play to hear more"
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I was so grateful to make the safety plan with my teen. I thought I knew which areas are safe for my teen and which are not. But when we made the safety plan together, I realised that my girl knew more areas that I was not aware of.\n"
"\n"
"I also thought she was safe at school, but through this activity I realised she was being bullied and the teachers did not do anything about it.\n"
"\n"
"The more we talked, the more I understood and got information from my teen. That really helped me to protect my teen and keep her safe."
msgstr ""

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"The most important way to help keep your teen safe is to make sure that they know they can talk to you about anything. \n"
"\n"
"Work with your teen to notice risks — like when someone pressures or makes them feel uncomfortable, online or offline.\n"
"\n"
"**Let’s look at examples of risky situations to help you spot warning signs.**"
msgstr ""

